        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-item">
          <div class="feature-text">
            <h3>Mobile App</h3>
            <p>You will get mobile app installable in your mobile for your demo.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item">
          <div class="feature-text">
            <h3>Documentation</h3>
            <p>Which includes 12 chapters like Abstract, Modules & UML diagrams with 40 - 50 pages.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Center Image -->
      <div class="feature-image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555774698-0b77e0d5fac6?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="App Development" />
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column -->
      <div class="feature-col right">
        <div class="feature-item">
          <div class="feature-icon">
             <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-text">
            <h3>Installation & Configuration</h3>
            <p>We will do installation & configuration the project in your laptop/pc.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-text">
            <h3>Explanation & Demo</h3>
            <p>We access your computer through anydesk and we will show the demo.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83 2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83l.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33-1.82 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2-2h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83 2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0l.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82.33H9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2 2v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83l-.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33 1.82V9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-text">
            <h3>Support & Guideline</h3>
            <p>We support by Email, Call and Chat guidelines of projects execution.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-center" style="margin-top: 50px;">
       <a href="/about" class="btn-more">MORE ABOUT US</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why-choose-us {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #fff;
  }
  .section-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .features-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center; /* Center vertically */
  }

  .feature-col {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .feature-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .left .feature-item {
    flex-direction: row;
    text-align: right;
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }
  
  .right .feature-item {
    flex-direction: row;
    text-align: left;
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }

  /* Text Styling */
  .feature-text h3 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    color: #7cb342; /* Green */
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .feature-text p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #333;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Icons */
  .feature-icon {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #333;
  }

  /* Center Image */
  .feature-image {
    flex: 0 0 450px; /* Increased width */
    width: 450px;
    margin: 0 20px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .feature-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); /* More refined shadow */
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .btn-more {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #8bc34a;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 12px 30px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .btn-more:hover {
    background: #7cb342;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .features-wrapper {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 50px;
    }
    .feature-col {
      width: 100%;
    }
    .left .feature-item {
       flex-direction: row-reverse;
       text-align: left;
       justify-content: flex-start;
    }
    .left .feature-item .feature-text {
       text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>
